column5: Twice. During my first missed appointment, about 2 day notice. But my second appointment, my bf called that very morning, so none.
Ah, wait. Am I allowed to explain or do I have to accept my judgement?
I'm sorry it reads that way. That wasn't my intention.
I'm heading to campus for a class and to study a bit
You don't know how much I needed to hear that. Thank you.
Yeah, pretty much. I also eat a lot of nuts, chia seeds, granola-- all that crazy shit in the bulk bins lmao.
